{"title":"安装Office各版本及激活","uid":"ed85beca4e7f7155e8ad20a6dde42cab","slug":"InstallandActiveOffice","date":"2022-10-25T14:10:00.000Z","updated":"2022-10-25T15:24:10.912Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/InstallandActiveOffice.json","keywords":null,"cover":[],"content":"<div class=\"custom-quote tip\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12.01 15C12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5 12.01 14.5C12.04 13.75 13 13.46 14.04 12.2C14.41 11.74 14.69 11.41 14.86 10.85C15.15 9.95 14.92 9.18 14.86 9.02C14.8 8.79 14.52 8 13.72 7.46C13.06 7.02 12.42 7 12.14 7C11.9 7 11.36 7 10.78 7.3C10.28 7.56 9.98 7.9 9.83 8.1C9.24 8.82 9.06 9.63 9 10.06\"></path>\n<path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M11.99 18H12.01\"></path>\n</svg></span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">阅读前提</p>\n<p>阅读以下内容时，请先保证你有足够脑容量来吸收此内容<br>且保证能按照步骤完整做完<br>本教程足够傻瓜，且包教包会，不懂再问</p>\n</div>\n<p><strong>首先须知</strong><br>要装Office的原因大部分应该都是课程需要或需要考试，首先你得了解目前阶段的考试需要那些Office的组件<br>据我所知，目前阶段的考试应该需要的组件有以下几个,且版本要求为Office 2016(VOLPLUS或其他含有Access的版本)</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Access（数据库）</li>\n<li>Word（文档）</li>\n<li>Excel（表格）</li>\n<li>Powerpoint（幻灯片演示【俗称PPT】）<br>首先访问<a href=\"https://otp.landian.vip/\">Office Tool Plus</a>下载OTP工具<br><img src=\"https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/6357f36216f2c2beb1009bb9.png\" alt=\"1-1\"><br>在顶部找到下载页面<br><img src=\"https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/6357f36216f2c2beb1009b73.png\" alt=\"1-2\"><br>优先选择<strong>【包含框架 (ZIP 压缩包)】</strong>的版本，然后选一种<strong>合适的下载方式</strong><br>个人建议使用<strong>云图小镇</strong>或<strong>山东大学镜像站</strong>【比较稳定】<br>下载完成之后请将下载到的压缩包解压到自己看的到的地方，不用担心放不下，安装完Office 2016之后可以删除<br>解压完成之后，<strong>请打开文件夹内的Office Tool Plus，而不是.console的那个</strong><br><img src=\"https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/6357f36216f2c2beb1009b7d.png\" alt=\"1-3\"><br>进入Office Tool Plus之后，请按照下图中箭头顺序点击</li>\n</ul>\n<div class=\"custom-quote warning\">\n<span class=\"custom-quote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M20.86 14.13C20 14.7 19.56 15.74 19.77 16.76C20.13 18.55 18.55 20.13 16.76 19.77C15.74 19.57 14.7 20 14.13 20.86C13.12 22.38 10.89 22.38 9.88 20.86C9.3 20 8.26 19.56 7.24 19.77C5.45 20.13 3.87 18.55 4.23 16.76C4.43 15.74 4 14.7 3.14 14.13C1.62 13.12 1.62 10.89 3.14 9.88C4 9.3 4.44 8.26 4.23 7.24C3.87 5.45 5.45 3.87 7.24 4.23C8.26 4.44 9.3 4 9.87 3.14C10.88 1.62 13.11 1.62 14.12 3.14C14.7 4 15.74 4.44 16.76 4.23C18.55 3.87 20.13 5.45 19.77 7.24C19.56 8.26 20 9.3 20.86 9.87C22.38 10.88 22.38 13.12 20.86 14.13Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 8V13\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M12 15.99V16.01\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span>\n<p class=\"custom-quote-title\">注意</p>\n<p>首次打开该软件应该会让你同意一个东西，无脑点同意就行<br>部分电脑会显示成英文，但按钮位置不变，不懂可以私下问我<br>英文：同意协议——Agree</p>\n</div>\n<p><img src=\"https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/6357f36216f2c2beb1009b90.png\" alt=\"1-4\"><br>下一步，很关键，请按照下图中设置你要安装的Office版本之类的配置<br><img src=\"https://pic1.imgdb.cn/item/6357f36216f2c2beb1009baa.png\" alt=\"1-5\"></p>\n<div cl